Ompompi bomile emagcekeni, amanzi sawagcina ngo-2014 kuzoba wukhetho lukazwelonke. Uma udinga amanzi kufanele uyogwedla ipitsi. Kuyathusa ukuthi eminyakeni engu-24 kusekhona abantu abaswele amanzi nezindlu zomxhaso. Amaloli aletha amanzi afika kanye emuva kwezinyanga ezimbili. Izindlu zomxhaso zabhaliswa, kwafakwa izinombolo, kwakhiwa zangaphela, kume izindonga nje. Lokho-ke kushiya imibuzo yokuthi imali eyayikhishelwe ukwakhela abantu izindlu yashonaphi. Ngiyafisa ukuba izikhulu zomnyango oqondene nokunikezelwa kwamanzi emphakathini nezomnyango wezezindlu zike zivakashele eCinci zibone usizi esikulo.  Robert Mdladla ECINCI